# CC57  - Footswitch 9/10
# CC58  - Footswitch 10/11
# CC59  - EXP Toe Switch
# CC60  - Looper Record/Overdub
# CC61  - Looper Play/Stop
# CC62  - Looper Play Once
# CC63  - Looper Undo/Redo
